# HAE agents

Read root `CLAUDE.md` and `AGENTS.md`. Detailed rules: `.claude/rules/`. Workflows: `.claude/skills/*/SKILL.md`.

- Match existing app patterns; use `@hae/ui`, `@hae/firebase`, `@hae/branding`.
- HAE crimson/Inter UI — no generic purple/glow redesigns.
- Keep `firestore.rules` in sync; public EiR stays public.
- Default deploy is hosting + rules; functions need Blaze and must not block hosting CI.
- Confirm CI deploy before telling users a site change is live.
